title: Aerosoft - Ayers Rock X FSX / P3D / P3Dv2
description:
Fly to Australia`s most recognizable natural landmark, the large sandstone rock formation also known as Ayers Rock or Uluru. You can land at Connellan Airport (IATA: AYQ, ICAO: YAYE) a neat airport suitable for jets up to the Boeing 737-800. It handles around 300.000 passengers a year which mainly stay at the "city" of Ulara also featured in this scenery.

If youÃ‚Â´ve never been there, well, this is your chance. Hop on a plane and fly from Sydney, Melbourne, Darwin or Alice Springs and go rock climbing on one of the most famous sandstones!

Features:

Ayers Rock (YAYE) Connellan Airport plus surrounding scenery
Photo-real terrain and buildings textures
Fully accurate rendition of Connellan Airport
Realistic shadow rendition on all 3D objects and ground
Highly realistic night lighting environment
High resolution textures (2048pix)
Landmarks (Uluru, Kata Tjuta, villages,...) included
Pilot-activated runway lights (COM1 120.60)
Performance optimised scenery with no need for additional adjustments
Compatible with all known add-ons, including ftx Australia and all other ftx products
